                <div class="blog_footer_week">Week 3</div>
                <h2>Finding A New Need</h2>
                <p>What a difference a week makes! Our team always learns so much from research, and this week was no exception. Through recruiting and interviewing users and conducting secondary research, we came to the end of our first summer sprint with a focused need to guide us through the rest of the project.</p>
